data.description: Attention buyers!!  Sellers are willing to give a full priced, qualified buyer up to $10,000 towards closing costs/rate buy down!!Welcome to the Black Oak neighborhood in Lampe, Mo!!Nightly rental approved cabin!!This charming lake property has so much to offer, that you just have to come see it for yourself!!Make sure to watch the live video walkthrough on the second frame!!The completely updated A frame villa offers one bedroom, a large loft (currently used as additional bedroom), one bathroom, a sitting area with a fire pit, and a huge shop!!One of the biggest features this property has to offer is that....It's nightly rental approved!! This property can be used as a personal residence, vacation home, or an income producing opportunity!!The shop features a 15'x33' lower level, and a 12'x33' loft that could be converted to another livable space!!This villa has been meticulously cared for inside and out, and will be maintenance free!! Some updates include: new HVAC, new entry doors with keypad entry, powder coated spiral staircase, and new deck boards!!When you're looking for a nice neighborhood on the lake, look no further! There is a boat ramp in the neighborhood too!This one won't last long! Call today to schedule your private showing!!
